 best documentaries, interviews, and concerts from around the world are on CEEK now, with greater top performances being added regularly. \n\nCEEK VR is the definitive destination for exciting music concerts and premium entertainment experiences in Virtual Reality.", "short_description": "CEEK VR VENUES magnifies and transforms your phone into the most engulfing VR Concert Arena."}]}, "developer_name": "CEEK VR Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.ceek.com/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://ceek.com/terms", "publisher_name": "CEEK VR Inc", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://ceek.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME", "MOVIE", "MUSIC_VIDEO"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "253546533592781"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974607_428143398008493_8797652043796840448_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1klATMOO61wQ7kNvgEepR5N&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAwtn0I2Bzlbtt7_RD3EDqqtQC8wzzRjKQ-Ja1fqOR87Q&oe=678637D2"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "CEEK Virtual Reality", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1562173200, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "1921918521192813", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"appli